    my-vignette

    my-vignette.Rmd
    library(ignobioR)

    Prepare the data

    data(datashort) # Upload the dataset with occurrence data
head(datashort)
#>                                Taxon     Long      Lat uncertainty year
#> 1                Periploca graeca L. 10.36099 43.49084         300 2017
#> 2 Hermodactylus tuberosus (L.) Mill. 11.31946 43.34094         300 1858
#> 3              Schoenus nigricans L. 11.62055 43.03101         300 1860
#> 4 Hermodactylus tuberosus (L.) Mill. 11.04073 43.47003         300 1898
#> 5     Lepidium draba L. subsp. draba 11.43845 43.35579         300 1981
#> 6     Lepidium draba L. subsp. draba 11.43015 43.32769         300 1986

data(site) # Upload the study area
data(exclareas) # Unsuitable data

sp::plot(site)
sp::plot(exclareas, add=TRUE, col="red")

    Draft the virtual floristic list (VFL)

    vfl <- virtual_list(data_flor=datashort, site=site, excl_areas=exclareas, tau=20)
